        "subject": "LU-8304 libcfs: Do not call kthread_run in wrong state",
        "message": "LU-8304 libcfs: Do not call kthread_run in wrong state\n\nkthread_run might sleep during an allocation, and so\nit's considered unsafe to call with a state that's not\nRUNNABLE. Move the state setting to after kthread_run call.\n\nChange-Id: I8d0694402990e6f688a0d1dfe8597ffe45c18962\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
